AXS-696x418.jpg 696w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Inside-3T-Cycling-Factory-Tour_How-3T-Torno-carbon-cranks-are-made-by-hand_made-in-Italy_2020-3T-Exploro-Team-Force-Eagle-AXS-1068x641.jpg 1068w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Inside-3T-Cycling-Factory-Tour_How-3T-Torno-carbon-cranks-are-made-by-hand_made-in-Italy_2020-3T-Exploro-Team-Force-Eagle-AXS-700x420.jpg 700w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Inside-3T-Cycling-Factory-Tour_How-3T-Torno-carbon-cranks-are-made-by-hand_made-in-Italy_2020-3T-Exploro-Team-Force-Eagle-AXS.jpg 1500w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/2020-3T-Exploro-RaceMax-aero-gravel-bike_all-new-aerodynamic-carbon-gravel-race-bikeRealFast_climbing.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"560\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/2020-3T-Exploro-RaceMax-aero-gravel-bike_all-new-aerodynamic-carbon-gravel-race-bikeRealFast_climbing-800x560.jpg\" alt=\"2020 3T Exploro RaceMax aero gravel bike, all-new aerodynamic carbon gravel race bikeRealFast\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/2020-3T-Exploro-RaceMax-aero-gravel-bike_all-new-aerodynamic-carbon-gravel-race-bikeRealFast_climbing-800x560.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/2020-3T-Exploro-RaceMax-aero-gravel-bike_all-new-aerodynamic-carbon-gravel-race-bikeRealFast_climbing-297x208.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/2020-3T-Exploro-RaceMax-aero-gravel-bike_all-new-aerodynamic-carbon-gravel-race-bikeRealFast_climbing-120x84.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/2020-3T-Exploro-RaceMax-aero-gravel-bike_all-new-aerodynamic-carbon-gravel-race-bikeRealFast_climbing-768x538.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/2020-3T-Exploro-RaceMax-aero-gravel-bike_all-new-aerodynamic-carbon-gravel-race-bikeRealFast_climbing.jpg 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/3T-Exploro-RaceMax-Boost-gravel-e-bike_hidden-ebikemotion-X35_riding-e-gravel.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/3T-Exploro-RaceMax-Boost-gravel-e-bike_hidden-ebikemotion-X35_riding-e-gravel-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"3T Exploro Race Max Boost gravel e-bike powered by ebikemotion, riding\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/3T-Exploro-RaceMax-Boost-gravel-e-bike_hidden-ebikemotion-X35_riding-e-gravel-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/3T-Exploro-RaceMax-Boost-gravel-e-bike_hidden-ebikemotion-X35_riding-e-gravel-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/3T-Exploro-RaceMax-Boost-gravel-e-bike_hidden-ebikemotion-X35_riding-e-gravel-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/3T-Exploro-RaceMax-Boost-gravel-e-bike_hidden-ebikemotion-X35_riding-e-gravel-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/3T-Exploro-RaceMax-Boost-gravel-e-bike_hidden-ebikemotion-X35_riding-e-gravel-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/3T-Exploro-RaceMax-Boost-gravel-e-bike_hidden-ebikemotion-X35_riding-e-gravel.jpg 1500w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/3T-Exploro-Ultra-carbon-adventure-aero-gravel-bikepacking-bike_Copper-complete.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/3T-Exploro-Ultra-carbon-adventure-aero-gravel-bikepacking-bike_Copper-complete-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"3T Exploro Ultra carbon adventure aero gravel bikepacking bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/3T-Exploro-Ultra-carbon-adventure-aero-gravel-bikepacking-bike_Copper-complete-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/3T-Exploro-Ultra-carbon-adventure-aero-gravel-bikepacking-bike_Copper-complete-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/3T-Exploro-Ultra-carbon-adventure-aero-gravel-bikepacking-bike_Copper-complete-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/3T-Exploro-Ultra-carbon-adventure-aero-gravel-bikepacking-bike_Copper-complete-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/3T-Exploro-Ultra-carbon-adventure-aero-gravel-bikepacking-bike_Copper-complete-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/3T-Exploro-Ultra-carbon-adventure-aero-gravel-bikepacking-bike_Copper-complete-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/3T-Exploro-Ultra-carbon-adventure-aero-gravel-bikepacking-bike_Copper-complete.jpg 1800w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/2020-3T-Exploro-RaceMax-aero-gravel_aerodynamic-carbon-gravel-bike_wet-bikepacking.jpg\"><img width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/2020-3T-Exploro-RaceMax-aero-gravel_aerodynamic-carbon-gravel-bike_wet-bikepacking.jpg\" alt=\"2020 3T Exploro RaceMax aero gravel bike, aerodynamic carbon gravel bike review, Exploro Race GRX 2x complete\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/2020-3T-Exploro-RaceMax-aero-gravel_aerodynamic-carbon-gravel-bike_wet-bikepacking.jpg 1200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/2020-3T-Exploro-RaceMax-aero-gravel_aerodynamic-carbon-gravel-bike_wet-bikepacking-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/2020-3T-Exploro-RaceMax-aero-gravel_aerodynamic-carbon-gravel-bike_wet-bikepacking-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/2020-3T-Exploro-RaceMax-aero-gravel_aerodynamic-carbon-gravel-bike_wet-bikepacking-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/2020-3T-Exploro-RaceMax-aero-gravel_aerodynamic-carbon-gravel-bike_wet-bikepacking-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/2020-3T-Exploro-RaceMax-aero-gravel_aerodynamic-carbon-gravel-bike_wet-bikepacking-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photos/Cory Benson)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The 3T Exploro has been around as an <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/3t-hits-the-gravel-with-all-new-multi-surface-exploro-carbon-frame-and-650b-wheels-first-look/\" target=\"_blank\">aero gravel bike since 2016</a>. And, I’ve ridden every generation since – at least 5 or 6 different Exploros with one inelegant cable routing solution. The RaceMax platform itself, has been <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/all-new-3t-exploro-racemax-hones-aero-gravel-with-wide-tire-specific-aerodynamics/\">around for 4 years</a>, now. I reviewed this latest bike <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/review-the-new-3t-exploro-racemax-is-every-bit-the-capable-gravel-racer-now-even-faster/\" target=\"_blank\">back in the summer of 2020</a>. And all-in-all I think it’s still one of the best, most versatile but still race-ready gravel bikes out there. Well, except for one major nit I had to pick…</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/2020-3T-Exploro-RaceMax-aero-gravel_aerodynamic-carbon-gravel-bike_cable-routing.jpg\"><img width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/2020-3T-Exploro-RaceMax-aero-gravel_aerodynamic-carbon-gravel-bike_cable-routing.jpg\" alt=\"2020 3T Exploro RaceMax aero gravel bike, aerodynamic carbon gravel bike review, Exploro Race GRX 2x complete\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/2020-3T-Exploro-RaceMax-aero-gravel_aerodynamic-carbon-gravel-bike_cable-routing.jpg 1200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/2020-3T-Exploro-RaceMax-aero-gravel_aerodynamic-carbon-gravel-bike_cable-routing-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/2020-3T-Exploro-RaceMax-aero-gravel_aerodynamic-carbon-gravel-bike_cable-routing-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/2020-3T-Exploro-RaceMax-aero-gravel_aerodynamic-carbon-gravel-bike_cable-routing-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/2020-3T-Exploro-RaceMax-aero-gravel_aerodynamic-carbon-gravel-bike_cable-routing-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/2020-3T-Exploro-RaceMax-aero-gravel_aerodynamic-carbon-gravel-bike_cable-routing-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a><figcaption>2020 Exploro RaceMax’s worst feature <em>(Photo/Cory Benson)</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The cable routing into the frame just behind the headset was simply bad. Always in the way, whether mounting devices over the stem or using any toptube bag. It was annoying enough that I wasn’t bothered when it was time to return that test bike to 3T. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2023-3T-Extrema-Italia-First-Rides-Review_new-carbon-29er-XC-tire-aero-adventure-bikepacking-gravel-bike-made-in-Italy_direct-mount-toptuba-bag-placement.jpg\"><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2023-3T-Extrema-Italia-First-Rides-Review_new-carbon-29er-XC-tire-aero-adventure-bikepacking-gravel-bike-made-in-Italy_direct-mount-toptuba-bag-placement.jpg\" alt=\"2023 3T Exploro Extrema Italia First Rides Review, new carbon 29er XC 29x2.25&quot; MTB tire aero adventure bikepacking gravel bike, top tube bag mount\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2023-3T-Extrema-Italia-First-Rides-Review_new-carbon-29er-XC-tire-aero-adventure-bikepacking-gravel-bike-made-in-Italy_direct-mount-toptuba-bag-placement.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2023-3T-Extrema-Italia-First-Rides-Review_new-carbon-29er-XC-tire-aero-adventure-bikepacking-gravel-bike-made-in-Italy_direct-mount-toptuba-bag-placement-297x165.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2023-3T-Extrema-Italia-First-Rides-Review_new-carbon-29er-XC-tire-aero-adventure-bikepacking-gravel-bike-made-in-Italy_direct-mount-toptuba-bag-placement-800x444.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2023-3T-Extrema-Italia-First-Rides-Review_new-carbon-29er-XC-tire-aero-adventure-bikepacking-gravel-bike-made-in-Italy_direct-mount-toptuba-bag-placement-120x67.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2023-3T-Extrema-Italia-First-Rides-Review_new-carbon-29er-XC-tire-aero-adventure-bikepacking-gravel-bike-made-in-Italy_direct-mount-toptuba-bag-placement-768x427.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2023-3T-Extrema-Italia-First-Rides-Review_new-carbon-29er-XC-tire-aero-adventure-bikepacking-gravel-bike-made-in-Italy_direct-mount-toptuba-bag-placement-1536x853.jpg 1536w\" /></a><figcaption>2023 3T Exploro Extrema Italia solved the internal routing problem, but was expensive <em>(Photo/Cory Benson)</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>And I was genuinely psyched <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/3t-extrema-italia-carbon-29er-adventure-gravel-bike/\" target=\"_blank\">when I first rode</a> the made-in-Italy <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/3t-extrema-italia-gets-faster-gnarlier-for-gravel-bike-adventure-racing/\" target=\"_blank\">Exploro Extrema Italia</a> which fixed the internal cable routing issue (<em>even if the toptube bolts didn’t exactly seem to be in the correct spot</em>). </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sure, it meant that the new made-in-Italy bikes were only compatible with electronic shift drivetrains. And they were a lot more expensive. But, it was so much better a solution that this was a gravel bike I would like to keep around for a bit longer.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/3T-RaceMax-WPNT-Integrale-aero-carbon-gravel-bike-gets-integrated_We-Paint-in-Italy-jpg.webp\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/3T-RaceMax-WPNT-Integrale-aero-carbon-gravel-bike-gets-integrated_We-Paint-in-Italy-jpg.webp\" alt=\"3T RaceMax WPNT Integrale aero carbon gravel bike gets integrated, We Paint frames on a rack\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/3T-RaceMax-WPNT-Integrale-aero-carbon-gravel-bike-gets-integrated_We-Paint-in-Italy-jpg.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/3T-RaceMax-WPNT-Integrale-aero-carbon-gravel-bike-gets-integrated_We-Paint-in-Italy-297x267.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/3T-RaceMax-WPNT-Integrale-aero-carbon-gravel-bike-gets-integrated_We-Paint-in-Italy-1536x1382.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/3T-RaceMax-WPNT-Integrale-aero-carbon-gravel-bike-gets-integrated_We-Paint-in-Italy-120x108.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/3T-RaceMax-WPNT-Integrale-aero-carbon-gravel-bike-gets-integrated_We-Paint-in-Italy-768x691.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Now, that’s no longer holding it back, I can say this made-in-Taiwan RaceMax is one of the best all-rounder gravel bikes out there. It does everything the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/3t-exploro-racemax-italia-exposes-raw-carbon-weave/\" target=\"_blank\">RaceMax Italia</a> does – the same shaping, tire sizes, component standards, and geometry – just with a frameset that costs half as much built with pre-preg carbon instead of filament winding.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>2025 3T RaceMax WPNT Integrale – Pricing, options &amp; availability</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/3T-RaceMax-WPNT-Integrale-aero-carbon-gravel-bike-gets-integrated_frameset-Avorio-off-white-jpg.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"1152\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/3T-RaceMax-WPNT-Integrale-aero-carbon-gravel-bike-gets-integrated_frameset-Avorio-off-white-1536x1152.webp\" alt=\"3T RaceMax WPNT Integrale, angled front Avorio white\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/3T-RaceMax-WPNT-Integrale-aero-carbon-gravel-bike-gets-integrated_frameset-Avorio-off-white-1536x1152.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/3T-RaceMax-WPNT-Integrale-aero-carbon-gravel-bike-gets-integrated_frameset-Avorio-off-white-297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/3T-RaceMax-WPNT-Integrale-aero-carbon-gravel-bike-gets-integrated_frameset-Avorio-off-white-120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/3T-RaceMax-WPNT-Integrale-aero-carbon-gravel-bike-gets-integrated_frameset-Avorio-off-white-768x576.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/3T-RaceMax-WPNT-Integrale-aero-carbon-gravel-bike-gets-integrated_frameset-Avorio-off-white-jpg.webp 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/3T-RaceMax-WPNT-Integrale-aero-carbon-gravel-bike-gets-integrated_frameset-Malva-purple-jpg.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"1152\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/3T-RaceMax-WPNT-Integrale-aero-carbon-gravel-bike-gets-integrated_frameset-Malva-purple-1536x1152.webp\" alt=\"3T RaceMax WPNT Integrale, frameset Malva purple\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/3T-RaceMax-WPNT-Integrale-aero-carbon-gravel-bike-gets-integrated_frameset-Malva-purple-1536x1152.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/3T-RaceMax-WPNT-Integrale-aero-carbon-gravel-bike-gets-integrated_frameset-Malva-purple-297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/3T-RaceMax-WPNT-Integrale-aero-carbon-gravel-bike-gets-integrated_frameset-Malva-purple-120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/3T-RaceMax-WPNT-Integrale-aero-carbon-gravel-bike-gets-integrated_frameset-Malva-purple-768x576.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/3T-RaceMax-WPNT-Integrale-aero-carbon-gravel-bike-gets-integrated_frameset-Malva-purple-jpg.webp 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/3T-RaceMax-WPNT-Integrale-aero-carbon-gravel-bike-gets-integrated_frameset-Mara-blue-jpg.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"1152\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/3T-RaceMax-WPNT-Integrale-aero-carbon-gravel-bike-gets-integrated_frameset-Mara-blue-1536x1152.webp\" alt=\"3T RaceMax WPNT Integrale, angled rear Mara blue\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/3T-RaceMax-WPNT-Integrale-aero-carbon-gravel-bike-gets-integrated_frameset-Mara-blue-1536x1152.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/3T-RaceMax-WPNT-Integrale-aero-carbon-gravel-bike-gets-integrated_frameset-Mara-blue-297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/3T-RaceMax-WPNT-Integrale-aero-carbon-gravel-bike-gets-integrated_frameset-Mara-blue-120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/3T-RaceMax-WPNT-Integrale-aero-carbon-gravel-bike-gets-integrated_frameset-Mara-blue-768x576.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/3T-RaceMax-WPNT-Integrale-aero-carbon-gravel-bike-gets-integrated_frameset-Mara-blue-jpg.webp 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The newly integrated RaceMax WPNT is <a href=\"https://3t.bike/collections/racemax-wpnt\" target=\"_blank\">now available directly from 3T</a> in 5 special edition paint colors: Camo gray, Indaco blue, Mara blue, Malva purple &amp; Avorio off-white. And it is offered both as a 2975€ frameset, or a complete bike build for 6150€ with a new GRX Di2 2x build and aero carbon 3T Discus 40/30 wheels. Either way featuring the 3T Fango RaceMax Integrale compact crown fork &amp; Apto Integrale Stealth stem to route all cables (electronic shift only) through the headet.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/3T-RaceMax-WPNT-Integrale-aero-carbon-gravel-bike-gets-integrated_GRX-Indaco-complete-jpg.webp\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/3T-RaceMax-WPNT-Integrale-aero-carbon-gravel-bike-gets-integrated_GRX-Indaco-complete-jpg.webp\" alt=\"3T RaceMax WPNT Integrale aero carbon gravel bike gets integrated, complete\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/3T-RaceMax-WPNT-Integrale-aero-carbon-gravel-bike-gets-integrated_GRX-Indaco-complete-jpg.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/3T-RaceMax-WPNT-Integrale-aero-carbon-gravel-bike-gets-integrated_GRX-Indaco-complete-297x178.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/3T-RaceMax-WPNT-Integrale-aero-carbon-gravel-bike-gets-integrated_GRX-Indaco-complete-1536x922.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/3T-RaceMax-WPNT-Integrale-aero-carbon-gravel-bike-gets-integrated_GRX-Indaco-complete-120x72.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/3T-RaceMax-WPNT-Integrale-aero-carbon-gravel-bike-gets-integrated_GRX-Indaco-complete-768x461.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Both new iterations of the new 3T RaceMax WPNT Integrale are painted and built-to-order, with a 6-8 week lead time.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://3t.bike/\" target=\"_blank\"><em>3T.bike</em></a></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/3t-racemax-gravel-bike-combines-integrale-upgrade-at-lower-prices-new-wpnt-colors/\">3T RaceMax Gravel Bike Combines Integrale Upgrade at Lower Prices &amp; New WPNT Colors</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"9578844519947efc3028c68f01efdc5197bc0ecff423b59a88da0e3b18bc4b31","category":"Cycling"}